items.title: Tron Wiki
items.headline: Tron Wiki
items.desc: TRON Wiki strives to be the definitive source of information on the TRON movies and the universe. TRON is a 1982 Disney science fiction film. It stars Jeff Bridges as Kevin Flynn/Clu, Bruce Boxleitner as Alan Bradley/Tron, Cindy Morgan as Lora Baines/Yori and Dan Shor as Popcorn Co-Worker/Ram. David Warner plays the villain, Ed Dillinger/Sark, as well as providing the voice of the Master Control Program. It was written and directed by Steven Lisberger. Being one of the first films in history to use 3-D computer graphics extensively, Tron has a distinctive visual style.

items.name: Jimmy Neutron Wiki
items.title: Jimmy Neutron Wiki
items.headline: Gotta Blast! Check out the Jimmy Neutron Wikia!
items.desc: '''Jimmy Neutron''' is a computer animated franchise produced for Nickelodeon. It tells the continuing saga of Jimmy Neutron, a teenage boy genius with an impossible IQ of 210 and his best friends having adventures together.

items.name: Voltron Wiki
items.title: Voltron Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to Voltron Wikia
items.desc: The Voltron Wiki is a community site dedicated to all things Voltron. If you are a fan of any of the Voltron incarnations, or even if you're just curious about them, then this is the place for you! Come explore our content and help us expand this database... or join us in discussion about the different TV series, the toys, the comics, or just Voltron in general. All are welcome!
